data.description: Check out this Two Story home on a corner lot! Unique feature of secret hidden storage underneath staircase behind shelving. 3 bedroom and 3 full baths. Backyard includes separate patio slab with wooden beams. No carpet, all solid flooring in the entire home. Buyers can receive an incentive of up to 1% back towards closing costs using preferred lender!!
